<p>Maybe you have a brilliant idea for your own add-on and no idea how to begin?</p>

<p>At this year&#8217;s EECI, we will have some of the most popular add-on developers in attendance, speaking, and socializing with the community.&nbsp; This is your chance to pull a developer aside and have that conversation you&#8217;ve long wished to have.</p>

<p>Some of our most prolific add-on developers will be attending EECI, including those who have built successful businesses around ExpressionEngine add-on development.&nbsp; This awe-inspiring list includes Mitchell Kimbrough, Brandon Kelly, Leevi Graham, Lodewijk Schutte, and many others ranging from highly successful developers to the budding enthusiast.</p>

<p>Join us at EECI to meet these amazing people, see just how approachable and friendly they are, learn both about add-on development and building a business around that add-on development, and have a fantastic time.</p>

<p><a href="http://eeci2010.com">See you there!</a></p>

