<p>Do you make some or all of your living deploying ExpressionEngine and/or CodeIgniter? Do you want an opportunity that has an unbelievably high return on investment for your time and money? Then please carefully consider this list of <a href="http://eeci2010.com/speakers/">EECI2010 speakers</a>:</strong> </p>

