</p>";}i:8;a:9:{s:5:"title";s:49:"Top Ten Reasons Why EECI is the Event of the Year";s:4:"link";s:56:"http://expressionengine.com/blog/entry/eeci2010_top_ten/";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:14:"Leslie Camacho";}s:8:"category";s:15:"NewsThe Insider";s:8:"comments";s:56:"http://expressionengine.com/blog/entry/eeci2010_top_ten/";s:11:"description";s:1617:"<p><a href="http://eeci2010.com/">EECI 2010 is closing in fast! Fortunately for you there are still tickets available</a>. In case you need some help deciding if spending time in one of the best cities in the US with the best professional community on the internet hosted by the gracious Robert Eerhart and Whoooz! Webmedia is worth your while, we&#8217;ve put together a Top Ten list for you. We&#8217;ll post 2-3 times a week until we&#8217;ve gone through them all. </p>

<p>10. <a href="http://expressionengine.com/blog/entry/10_rick_team/">Meet Rick Ellis &amp; The Team</a><br />
