<p>The highlight for us personally had to be Monday&#8217;s &#8220;ExpressionEngine 2.0: Total Domination&#8221; panel, with <a href="http://www.happycog.com/">Happy Cog</a> speakers Ryan Irelan, Jenn Lukas, Brian Warren, and Mark Huot, moderated by Kenny Meyers.&nbsp; This crew did such a fabulous job (neither authored nor even sponsored by EllisLab, incidentally) that SXSW staff were commenting about how it was the best panel they had seen all weekend.&nbsp; <a href="http://eeinsider.com/blog/sxsw-expressionengine-panel-slides/">The slides</a> will give you a summary of the content, but they can&#8217;t capture just how well each speaker brought their topics to life.</p>

